<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white><BR>
In re: to the rate she gives the Hoop, I can tell you that a good friend of mine got the hoop on his very first attempt!  He handed her a ruby and *poof*, there's the hoop.  He was a level 14 ogre warrior at the time.  I can also tell you that I've spoken to a peep who gave Lynuga 61 rubies before she got the hoop!  I think my buddy was just lucky as HELL! <BR>
<BR>
Oh, and good luck finding her...she spawns once every 24-48 hours and is often killed by goody-goody peeps...</font></td></tr></table>
