<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Rimamog</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-21 16:33:55</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes its true.  I, an Ogre of no small acclaim, landed the Hoop on the first try.  But, it took me two weeks of random wandering to find her.  Your best option is to stand out side of Guk and wait for her there.  All I know is I was AFK (Pinching a Loaf) and I heard I was being attacked.  I came running out, pants around ankles, and here was some loser elf yatch.  I killed her and then spotted Lynugas.  So, the moral of the story is not to wait for the elf to spawn.  The moral of the story is to go to the bathroom and Lynugas will show up...<BR>
<BR>
By the way, sold hoop for 2500pp.  Right before some dude offered way more than that! :(  <BR>
<BR>
Oh yeah, Hendryx is a Twink!</font></td></tr></table>
